{"tid":2100344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"曾國衛恐嚇市民初選或犯國安法","createTime":"2020-07-09T03:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T16:09:09.000Z","uid":123774,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e174eafa3511359ec8c79e96e0744a386b7f1b9","tid":2100344,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:44:48.000Z","msg":"曾國衞提醒組織活動的人士，《選舉(舞弊及非法行為)條例》內清楚列明選舉候選人的定義、選舉開支的規限等，除候選人本身及代理人外，其他人士在競選過程中產生選舉開支均屬違法，另條例亦有明確規定禁止在選舉期間進行某些活動等。他又指，組織、策劃及參與初選活動，有可能違反《港區國安法》第20條、第22條及第29條，一旦干犯，屬於嚴重罪行。他又呼籲市民參與初選時不要聚集，以免違反「禁聚令」，增加衞生風險，同時要留意主辦單位對個人資料是否有足夠保障。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200709/mobile/bkn-20200709000121092-0709_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200709%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200709000121092-0709_00822_001.html&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=26ba22c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200709/mobile/bkn-20200709000121092-0709_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜嘢國家先至會每日提住國安法去恐嚇市民<br />\n幾撚失敗失民心嘅政府先會淨低惡法及武力去管治<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>初選我實參與</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"90769f16853212f7cb84c673219c5efec402ab13","tid":2100344,"uid":8880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:45:51.000Z","msg":"佢地好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1573ea9ea2706068553b1ac07abb27024f4d3b80","tid":2100344,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:50:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8bad2ed7a04d16f250ef5662e55aca2e952640aa","tid":2100344,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:50:04.000Z","msg":"戴耀庭 嚴正反駁 曾國衛 對初選嘅指控<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2100288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2100288</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6cb6e2b5231e30468e4cefc294a26b2aacd8efa6",